room_title: Escape room "Quarantine" by The One 2 Escape Room in Miami
room_description: You are trapped in a CDC hospital quarantine room after being bitten by a zombie. You have an hour before the process is irreversible and you join the walking dead. You must take matters into your own hands and find a way to break into the laboratory and locate the antidote. You have only an hour to find the cure and escape with your life!
